<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096" id="mwBA">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" id="mwBQ">For the graduate textbook by Robert Wald, see <a href="General_Relativity_(book)" title="General Relativity (book)">General Relativity (book)</a>.</div>
