</div>

<p id="mwATw">On the left-hand side is the <a href="Einstein_tensor" title="Einstein tensor" id="mwAT0">Einstein tensor</a>, <span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwAT4"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle G_{\mu \nu }}">
