<dl id="mwAUA"><dd id="mwAUE"><span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwAUI"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle R=g^{\mu \nu }R_{\mu \nu }}">
