<p id="mwAUM">is the curvature scalar. The Ricci tensor itself is related to the more general <a href="Riemann_curvature_tensor" title="Riemann curvature tensor" id="mwAUQ">Riemann curvature tensor</a> as</p>
<dl id="mwAUU"><dd id="mwAUY"><span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwAUc"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle R_{\mu \nu }={R^{\alpha }}_{\mu \alpha \nu }.}">
