<p id="mwAUg">On the right-hand side, <span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwAUk"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \kappa }">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mi>κ<!-- κ --></mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \kappa }</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="../I/54ddec2e922c5caea4e47d04feef86e782dc8e6d.svg" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:1.339ex; height:1.676ex;" alt="\kappa " loading="lazy"></span> is a constant and <span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwAUo"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle T_{\mu \nu }}">
