<dl id="mwAVc"><dd id="mwAVg"><span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwAVk"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle R_{\mu \nu }=0.}">
