<p id="mwAXw">A conservative total <a href="Force" title="Force" id="mwAX0">force</a> can then be obtained as</p>

<dl id="mwAYA"><dd id="mwAYE"><span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwAYI"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle F_{f}(r)=-{\frac {GMm}{r^{2}}}+{\frac {L^{2}}{mr^{3}}}-{\frac {3GML^{2}}{mc^{2}r^{4}}}}">
