<p id="mwAoE">where:</p>
<ul id="mwAoI"><li id="mwAoM"><span class="mwe-math-element" id="mwAoQ"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle L}">
