</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:6em;text-align:center;"><a href="Exact_solutions_in_general_relativity" title="Exact solutions in general relativity">Solutions</a></th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-odd" style="padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
<ul><li>Cosmological: <a href="Friedmann%E2%80%93Lema%C3%AEtre%E2%80%93Robertson%E2%80%93Walker_metric" title="Friedmann–Lemaître–Robertson–Walker metric">Friedmann–Lemaître–Robertson–Walker</a> (<a href="Friedmann_equations" title="Friedmann equations">Friedmann equations</a>)</li>
